{"tid":226311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日香港已經唔係比香港人住，係蝻同蝗","createTime":"2017-05-02T12:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T15:58:00.000Z","uid":30694,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9efdc2d795c34eaad859db0d56decd880a42433e","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"雖然由回歸嗰日開始已經係，但係到今時今日問題已經非常嚴重，每日150同新移民唔再講，最大問題係蝻，佢地係社會一個大毒瘤，大炸彈，深水埗係集中地就大家都知，但而家出街去到邊都會見到蝻，甚至我隔離屋都係蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋邨所有設施全部都係啲蝻霸晒，不論公園/球場，成日見到佢地拎住啲球棒，係度嚇鳩啲細路，搞到人地唔撚敢再去，球場又聯黨結隊霸住晒，我今日跑完步見到4個蝻既細路，係度踢撚住波去球場，佢地仲啤鳩住我，想省鳩我，係我面前起腳但唔撚敢射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一班咁既垃圾種族夾埋幾個至幾廿個人去恰鳩人，就好似深水埗嗰單咁，40個人斬10幾個人，到時真係隨便出街都會比佢地斬，香港唔係比香港人住，所有公共設施亦都唔係比香港人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41645802cd6f46d6a30bbac9070e6c4fd4b22a1b","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲蝻真係社會毒瘤，冇貢獻"},{"pid":"892502e2e42ae66c45bb3c9ca8978fa6b57cdedb","tid":226311,"uid":55232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"觀塘球場果班垃圾蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d03460527f657ed6369a0c0573c2dcdf11756b1","tid":226311,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:25:11.000Z","msg":"蝻真係垃圾嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9b73335601a70d44f0bde7cb3a65cc3947f61e","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>觀塘球場果班垃圾蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全撚部都係垃圾，霸撚晒啲公共設施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b583633396428d0040de151c43bd8b415d4390","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝻真係垃圾嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係諗唔撚到有咩垃圾得過蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd04f8519395c56c85e3674d1fb499d184c66d89","tid":226311,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f48046a95bccae7e9d5fa6eca2fbdee602d1211d","tid":226311,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"可以以毒攻毒對付蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc3cdc0ec7b41e5153408a172205c9cd4f99677","tid":226311,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝難民之父張超雄</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"afbcdae101ee9face1bf8af891e76cb5c2ddd953","tid":226311,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa4c963d85ff84b71ef67f582f824c6682b7bd4","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上以前都唔覺咁多蝻狗, 近呢幾年突然多左好多, 多到我都醒覺, 唔可以再俾呢班仆街咁串</blockquote><br />\n多到有蝻住我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母咁易有屋住，我地香港人就等到死都未有，做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f79aaf9293de874b9378f52f0a4239e131af2e","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以以毒攻毒對付蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講蝻呢個毒瘤更大，已經係炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5152cd3b0c06e33c3692ef38223aef4814c935","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熟呢班仆街既人都知道佢地想鳩佔鵲巢, 成個香港想搶左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係，屌你老母行到邊都見到，所有球場公園都霸撚晒，仲係M記集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5352e09fff35ed0ce8c52b49ed90c215193bfb48","tid":226311,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c2831385bf3364b94a52236891699e4c5ae3b79","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>基本上以前都唔覺咁多蝻狗, 近呢幾年突然多左好多, 多到我都醒覺, 唔可以再俾呢班仆街咁串</blockquote><br />\n多到有蝻住我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母咁易有屋住，我地香港人就等到死都未有，做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陰謀論既話有機會係中共俾屋佢地住想清洗我地香港人, 好似俾蝗落黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以土生土長既蝻絕對係香港人大敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰啲所謂土生土長既蝻係到包庇佢地，係蝻就係蝻，一世都唔會變，仲想霸撚埋人地啲地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775a584fd6837b31ebfa15daf5eb7da1258df467","tid":226311,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:44:38.000Z","msg":"如果南亞人唔搞香港, 其實都有好處<br />\n可以睇佢地開片<br />\n<br />\n就好似前幾日, 有一單50南亞人街頭混戰, 好睇過電影"},{"pid":"94899d112a16f263326664da9c8b8f8cee56f560","tid":226311,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61ffa46b8347f39cae5012e283fc6a48181bab3a","tid":226311,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28ea333d4733206ea7b9391db0359c2221a72040","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果南亞人唔搞香港, 其實都有好處<br />\n可以睇佢地開片<br />\n<br />\n就好似前幾日, 有一單50南亞人街頭混戰, 好睇過電影</blockquote><br />\n屌 豬西出去先啦</blockquote><br />\n根本一放外族入黎就已經唔得，用酷刑聲請比班人落晒黎，拎我地資源，打家劫舍，強姦殺人咩都做，真係垃圾人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9eb022b4e2082bc981a7572e492af13e485671a","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>基本上以前都唔覺咁多蝻狗, 近呢幾年突然多左好多, 多到我都醒覺, 唔可以再俾呢班仆街咁串</blockquote><br />\n多到有蝻住我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母咁易有屋住，我地香港人就等到死都未有，做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陰謀論既話有機會係中共俾屋佢地住想清洗我地香港人, 好似俾蝗落黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以土生土長既蝻絕對係香港人大敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰啲所謂土生土長既蝻係到包庇佢地，係蝻就係蝻，一世都唔會變，仲想霸撚埋人地啲地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n土生土長既蝻根本係垃圾黎, 你依家周街見到聚哂係到鳩嗌鳩撞既蝻大多數都係有身份證既土生土長蝻</blockquote><br />\n所謂土生土長嗰班都係垃圾，自己群埋自己人去聯黨結隊，蝦蝦霸霸，就係利用酷刑聲請就可以落到黎，又有屋住，香港人就永遠都用唔到呢啲資源，比埋晒啲垃圾用，仲有啲大愛撚根本助長佢地既風氣，乜撚野識班垃圾好NICE，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93f94bbeb03d9890f957d3870afa440583be840","tid":226311,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"874bcaa4952f8c6bab0465136f493195d6e2964e","tid":226311,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果南亞人唔搞香港, 其實都有好處<br />\n可以睇佢地開片<br />\n<br />\n就好似前幾日, 有一單50南亞人街頭混戰, 好睇過電影</blockquote><br />\n屌 豬西出去先啦</blockquote><br />\n根本一放外族入黎就已經唔得，用酷刑聲請比班人落晒黎，拎我地資源，打家劫舍，強姦殺人咩都做，真係垃圾人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor